# Headers for the STANDALONE Sales OS Cloudflare Pages project (root dir = sales/).
# On the main site this file is just served as a static asset at /sales/_headers and is
# ignored; Cloudflare only applies the _headers found at a project's own build-output root.

# Internal tool. noindex is a crawl hint, NOT access control - this project still needs
# Cloudflare Access in front of it before sharing (it contains COGS, price floors, margins).
/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY

# HTML revalidates; it carries the ?v= content hashes that make the assets safely immutable.
/
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600, must-revalidate
/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600, must-revalidate

/*.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
/*.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
